ard DS the Pally.  I group with a druid all the time as well so with the cimbined DS I am getting 30 damage a hit extra.  Some of the mobs out there hit fast so this can add up quickly.  <br>
<br>
From what a guild bard was telling me if you have the Druid, or mage DS( they do not stack) along with the wizard DS(or shaman potion), coldain 8th ring and the bard DS you can put out around 100 a hit you take.  While this is the high end of possible damage.<br>
<br>
In the end especiually with the new spell set feature swapping out one spell at the start is easier then ever.  5hp extra damage may not sound like a lot but when you take into consideration the fact that in the 5 minutes the tank may be taking 50+ hits it adds up. <p><p><center><TABLE CELLPADDING="0" CELLSPACING="0" BORDER="0"><TR><TD><IMG 

